
Overview of noun scholar

The noun scholar has 3 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                        
1. (7) scholar, scholarly person, bookman, student -- (a learned person (especially in the humanities); someone who by long study has gained mastery in one or more disciplines)
2. (1) learner, scholar, assimilator -- (someone (especially a child) who learns (as from a teacher) or takes up knowledge or beliefs)
3. scholar -- (a student who holds a scholarship)
